{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't take long, because as we went across the lines to go to the other side of Birkenau, where the trains were supposed to take us to Germany, they didn't like the selection.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They saw that some people were not good enough for the work-- for work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they started, again, making a new selection, ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as we were in one, my sister, who was-- who was not as thin as I was-- she tried to-- she was in front of me, but she wanted to sort of hide-- to hide me.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans came over, divided us, and sent my sister to work, and me back away with all this-- with-- sorry to say, was-- was not good for work, with cripples.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, I-- I thought now, that's the end of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll never come out of this hell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a few girls-- they sent us to a cellar, which was like a garden room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half the window was in-- inside and half on top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was quite a dark room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of the girls opened the windows, and they ran out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was just sitting down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't want to do anything, because I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that point, I wasn't so strong, and I wasn't healthy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They can-- they can kill me if they-- if they get hold of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, after about four hours in there, we had no-- nothing to drink, nothing to eat, and it was so hot in August.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They got us to stand in fives again and marched us to the gates of Birkenau, but we were outside the gates of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
